x Journal Cover";s:4:"guid";s:20:"http://ma.tt/?p=6343";s:4:"link";s:41:"http://ma.tt/2008/06/linux-journal-cover/";s:11:"description";s:485:"<p><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/cover171.png" alt="" title="cover171" width="162" height="217" class="alignright size-full wp-image-6344" /> I was honored to be on the <a href="http://www.linuxjournal.com/issue/171">cover of Linux Journal this month</a> in an article by Katherine Druckman. Pick up a copy in your local enlightened bookstore or magazine shop. The article <a href="http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/10114">is available online to LJ subscribers here</a>.</p>";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Tue, 10 Jun 2008 10:33:35 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:4:"Matt";}s:7:"summary";s:485:"<p><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/cover171.png" alt="" title="cover171" width="162" height="217" class="alignright size-full wp-image-6344" /> I was honored to be on the <a href="http://www.linuxjournal.com/issue/171">cover of Linux Journal this month</a> in an article by Katherine Druckman. Pick up a copy in your local enlightened bookstore or magazine shop. The article <a href="http://www.linuxjournal.com/article/10114">is available online to LJ subscribers here</a>.</p>";}i:7;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:57:"Weblog Tools Collection: WordPress Theme Releases for 6/9";s:4:"guid";s:85:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/archives/2008/06/09/wordpress-theme-releases-for-69/";s:4:"link";s:85:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/archives/2008/06/09/wordpress-theme-releases-for-69/";s:11:"description";s:2511:"<h3>One Column Themes</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.junglejar.com/templates-in-a-jar/" target="_blank">Jin</a></p>\n<p><img title="jin-template" height="131" alt="jin-template" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/jintemplate.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Jin is a a one-column theme which allows users to add post images directly to the home page using the write post page. The theme has a extended sidebar in the footer area.</p>\n<h3>Two Column Themes</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.dailyblogtips.com/darkzen-wordpress-theme-released/" target="_blank"><strong>Darkzen</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="darkzen-thumbnail" height="126" alt="darkzen-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/darkzenthumbnail.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Darkzen is a two column widget-ready theme. The theme makes use of darker colors and comes built in with social networking integration for home pages as well as single pages.</p>\n<p><a href="http://everlong-design.com/resources/wordpress-themes/elegant-brit/" target="_blank"><strong>Elegant Brit</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="elegant-brit-thumbnail" height="94" alt="elegant-brit-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/elegantbritthumbnail.jpg" width="150" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Elegant Brit is a two column widget-ready theme. The theme allows visitors to rearrange the widgets in the sidebar as well as collapse any widgets that would not like to see. Users can store their settings for next time if cookies are enabled in the browser.</p>\n<p><a href="http://wplover.com/our-rights-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank"><strong>Our Rights</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="our-rights-thumbnail" height="161" alt="our-rights-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/ourrightsthumbnail.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Our Rights is a two column fixed-width widget-ready theme. The theme has in built support for Gravatars.</p>\n<h3>Three Column Themes</h3>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p><a href="http://ericulous.com/2008/05/28/wp-theme-technoholic-free-and-premium/" target="_blank"><strong>TechnoHolic</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="technoholic-thumbnail" height="119" alt="technoholic-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/technoholicthumbnail.png" width="199" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>TechnoHolic is a flexible three column theme which can also be converted into a two column theme. The theme also has a 3 column extended sidebar in the footer area.</p>";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Tue, 10 Jun 2008 03:54:00 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:12:"Keith Dsouza";}s:7:"summary";s:2511:"<h3>One Column Themes</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.junglejar.com/templates-in-a-jar/" target="_blank">Jin</a></p>\n<p><img title="jin-template" height="131" alt="jin-template" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/jintemplate.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Jin is a a one-column theme which allows users to add post images directly to the home page using the write post page. The theme has a extended sidebar in the footer area.</p>\n<h3>Two Column Themes</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.dailyblogtips.com/darkzen-wordpress-theme-released/" target="_blank"><strong>Darkzen</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="darkzen-thumbnail" height="126" alt="darkzen-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/darkzenthumbnail.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Darkzen is a two column widget-ready theme. The theme makes use of darker colors and comes built in with social networking integration for home pages as well as single pages.</p>\n<p><a href="http://everlong-design.com/resources/wordpress-themes/elegant-brit/" target="_blank"><strong>Elegant Brit</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="elegant-brit-thumbnail" height="94" alt="elegant-brit-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/elegantbritthumbnail.jpg" width="150" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Elegant Brit is a two column widget-ready theme. The theme allows visitors to rearrange the widgets in the sidebar as well as collapse any widgets that would not like to see. Users can store their settings for next time if cookies are enabled in the browser.</p>\n<p><a href="http://wplover.com/our-rights-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank"><strong>Our Rights</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="our-rights-thumbnail" height="161" alt="our-rights-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/ourrightsthumbnail.png" width="200" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>Our Rights is a two column fixed-width widget-ready theme. The theme has in built support for Gravatars.</p>\n<h3>Three Column Themes</h3>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p><a href="http://ericulous.com/2008/05/28/wp-theme-technoholic-free-and-premium/" target="_blank"><strong>TechnoHolic</strong></a></p>\n<p><img title="technoholic-thumbnail" height="119" alt="technoholic-thumbnail" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/b2-img/2008/06/technoholicthumbnail.png" width="199" border="0" /> </p>\n<p>TechnoHolic is a flexible three column theme which can also be converted into a two column theme. The theme also has a 3 column extended sidebar in the footer area.</p>";}i:8;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:22:"Matt: Santorini, Milos";s:4:"guid";s:20:"http://ma.tt/?p=6115";s:4:"link";s:37:"http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/";s:11:"description";s:16330:"<p>Final morning in Santorini, ferry ride, Milos.</p>\n<p><span id="more-6115"></span></p>\n\n<a href="http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/mcm_0933/" title="mcm_0933"><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/mcm_0933-195x129.jpg" width="195" height="129" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="" /></a>\n<a href="http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/mcm_0934/" title="mcm_0934"><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/mcm_0934-139x210.jpg" width="139" height="210" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="" /></a>\n<a href="http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/mcm_0935/" title="mcm_0935"><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/mcm_0935-195x129.jpg" width="195" height="129" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="" /></a>\n<a href="http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/mcm_0938/" title="mcm_0938"><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/mcm_0938-139x210.jpg" width="139" height="210" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="" /></a>\n<a href="http://ma.tt/2008/06/santorini-milos/mcm_0939/" title="mcm_0939"><img src="http://s.ma.tt/files/2008/06/mcm_0939-195x129.jpg" width="195" height="129" class="atta